 A fuel-laden tanker has gone up in flames at the Kara end of the Lagos-Ibadan Expressway.
According to reports, the tanker caught fire at about 1 am on Saturday.
The incident caused a massive gridlock especially for motorists travelling out of Lagos.
Eyewitnesses said some vehicles had been caught up in the inferno.
